        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14211",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gavin",
                        "name": "gavin",
                        "displayName": "Gavin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I expect people will be open to adding this.  A code submission would be appreciated :)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=gavin",
                        "name": "gavin",
                        "displayName": "Gavin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-16T13:10:34.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-16T13:10:34.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14214",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I think it should be added like Zend_Validate_Isbn but how we do the difference between ISBN-10 and ISBN-13 or is ISBN-10 deprecated enough that we can lose sight of? Or should we add Zend_Validate_Isbn_13Digits and Zend_Validate_Isbn_10Digits? Don\u00b4t know.\n\nWhat do you think?\n\nHere a small quick and dirty solution for ISBN-13 and ISBN-10 without formatting (and no check for valide input):\n{code}<?php\n\nfunction validateIsbn10($isbn)\n{   \n    $remainder = $isbn{9};\n    $checksum  = 0;\n    \n    for ($i=10, $a=0; $i>1; $i--, $a++)\n    {\n        $num       = $isbn{$a};\n        $checksum += $num * $i;\n    }\n    \n    return ((11 - ($checksum % 11)) == $remainder);\n}\n\nfunction validateIsbn13($isbn)\n{\n    $remainder = $isbn{12};\n    $checksum  = 0;\n    \n    for ($i=0; $i<12; $i++)\n    {\n        $multi     = (($i % 2) == 1) ? 1 : 3;\n        $num       = $isbn{$i};\n        $checksum += $num * $multi;\n    }\n    \n    return ((10 - ($checksum % 10)) == $remainder);\n}\n\n$isbn = '9783866400016';\nvar_dump(validateIsbn13($isbn)); \/\/ true\n\n$isbn = '0306406153';\nvar_dump(validateIsbn10($isbn)); \/\/ true\n\n?>{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-16T16:28:37.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-16T16:28:37.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14219",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mben",
                        "name": "mben",
                        "displayName": "Marc Bennewitz (GIATA mbH)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The Zend_Validate_Isbn can configure before which isbn versions are alowed.\n\n{code}\n$isbn13 = '9783866400016';\n$isbn10 = '0306406153';\n\n$validator = new Zend_Validate_Isbn();\n$validator ->allowVersion(10);\n$validator->isValid($isbn10); \/\/ true\n$validator->isValid($isbn13); \/\/ false\n\n$validator ->allowVersion(13);\n$validator->isValid($isbn10); \/\/ true\n$validator->isValid($isbn13); \/\/ true\n{code}\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mben",
                        "name": "mben",
                        "displayName": "Marc Bennewitz (GIATA mbH)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T03:43:47.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T03:43:47.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14220",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Attached propsal for Zend_Validate_Isbn.\n\n{code}$isbn13 = '9783866400016';\n$isbn10 = '0306406152';\n\n$oIsbn = new Zend_Validate_Isbn;\n$oIsbn->allowVersion(Zend_Validate_Isbn::ISBN13);\n\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13)); \/\/ true\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10)); \/\/ false\n\n$oIsbn->allowVersion(Zend_Validate_Isbn::ISBN10);\n\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10)); \/\/ true{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T04:38:41.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T04:38:41.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14222",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Attached new version of propsal (small changes).\n\n{code}require_once 'Zend\/Filter\/Digits.php';\n\n$isbn13  = '9783866400016';\n$isbn10  = '0306406152';\n$isbn13s = '978-3-866-40001-6';\n$isbn10s = '0-306-40615-2';\n\n$oDigits = new Zend_Filter_Digits();\n$isbn13sc = $oDigits->filter($isbn13s);\n$isbn10sc = $oDigits->filter($isbn10s);\n\n$oIsbn = new Zend_Validate_Isbn;\n$oIsbn->allowVersion(Zend_Validate_Isbn::ISBN13);\n\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13)); \/\/ true\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13s)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10s)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13sc)); \/\/ true\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10sc)); \/\/ false\n\n$oIsbn->allowVersion(Zend_Validate_Isbn::ISBN10);\n\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10)); \/\/ true\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13s)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10s)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn13sc)); \/\/ false\nvar_dump($oIsbn->isValid($isbn10sc)); \/\/ true{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T04:53:50.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T04:53:50.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14231",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mben",
                        "name": "mben",
                        "displayName": "Marc Bennewitz (GIATA mbH)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "In Zend_Validate_Isbn_V3.php:\nIt can test isbn numbers with valid string separators \" \" and \"-\" and the isbn can start wth \"isbn\"\nbecause it is a valid isbn and must not filtered to digits manuely.\nsecondary it can test a isbn by all versions in one call.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mben",
                        "name": "mben",
                        "displayName": "Marc Bennewitz (GIATA mbH)",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T10:46:33.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T10:46:33.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14236",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I like that you implemented sth. to validate the isbn generally and not only ISBN-10 *or* ISBN-13.\n\nI think we should split up filtering and validation. We can use filtering *in* validation but filtering should be in a seperate class (e.g. Zend_Filter_Isbn).",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jpieper",
                        "name": "jpieper",
                        "displayName": "Jan Pieper",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T12:35:16.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T12:35:16.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/14268",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bkarwin",
                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Assign to Darby.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bkarwin",
                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-04-17T19:20:33.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-04-17T19:20:33.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/15673",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=andries",
                        "name": "andries",
                        "displayName": "Andries Seutens",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "There's a proposal related to this \"issue\", which can be found [here|http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/wiki\/x\/W4g].\n\nPersonally, I don't like to see ISBN-10 and ISBN-13 wrapped in one class, they should be 2 seperate validators if you ask me. I also think that these validators should go under the Zend_Validate_Barcode_* namespace.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=andries",
                        "name": "andries",
                        "displayName": "Andries Seutens",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-07-03T09:26:23.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-07-03T09:26:23.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16433",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=darby",
